  <h3 class="margin">4 most influential guitars</h3>
  <img src="https://static.guitarcenter.com/riffs/binaries/content/gallery/guitarcenter/gibson-les-paul-goldtop.jpg" class="img-responsive img-circle margin" style="display:inline" width="550" height="350">
  <h3>Life wouldn't be the same without these</h3>
